Incident 02 - Persistence and Privilege Escalation

Summary
A local user account was created and later added to the Administrators group.

Evidence
Event ID 4720
Event ID 4732

Timeline
- User account created
- User added to Administrators group

Impact
Potential unauthorized administrative access.

MITRE ATT&CK
T1136.001 - Local Account
T1098 - Account Manipulation

Recommendation
Review account legitimacy and remove unauthorized privileges.
